paragraphs.title: ICA para 18 Meses Antes da Quebra
paragraphs.text: %sql select substring(data,0,10) data, case when avg(alerta2) OVER twenty_days > 0.05 then avg(alerta2) OVER twenty_days else 0.0 end AS ICA from (select data, sum(alerta) as alerta2 from consolidado where data < '2008-07-22' group by data order by data) as newtable WINDOW  twenty_days AS (ORDER BY data ROWS BETWEEN 21 PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW)
